      "comment": "BENNIE AND THE JETS NZ (9) continued his good form when he led and fought well to go under narrowly in this grade last start at Bendigo. Scored back-to-back wins at this venue prior, one of them from a similar barrier to this. Strong claims. HILLTOP HUGH (3) made a nice return at his latest appearance six weeks ago, finishing third at this circuit and distance. That was his first appearance since winning the Vicbred 4EG Final last November. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Major player. QUIRKY CHARACTER (7) may need a touch of luck from this draw but strikes at 50 per cent here. HEZA GUN (2) must be respected after scoring from a wider barrier last start by 1.6 metres at this venue.",
